"to\": 6856}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Instead, France signaled that the West is determined to continue its inexorable march into absolute hedonic madness.\", \"from\": 6873, \"to\": 6989, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6882, \"end\": 6888, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.6034505717697117, \"rank\": 0.6246964021154502, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the West\", \"from\": 6903, \"to\": 6911}, {\"ngram\": \"its inexorable march\", \"from\": 6938, \"to\": 6958}, {\"ngram\": \"absolute hedonic madness\", \"from\": 6964, \"to\": 6988}]}, {\"sentence\": \"If the Summer Olympics opening ceremony allows a nation to both reflect on its achievements and look hopefully toward its future, then this year's ceremony states in no uncertain terms that the West has no future.\", \"from\": 6990, \"to\": 7203, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Summer Olympics opening ceremony\", \"from\": 6993, \"to\": 7029}, {\"ngram\": \"a nation\", \"from\": 7037, \"to\": 7045}, {\"ngram\": \"its achievements\", \"from\": 7065, \"to\": 7081}, {\"ngram\": \"its future\", \"from\": 7108, \"to\": 7118}, {\"ngram\": \"no uncertain terms\", \"from\": 7156, \"to\": 7174}, {\"ngram\": \"the West\", \"from\": 7180, \"to\": 7188}, {\"ngram\": \"no future\", \"from\": 7193, \"to\": 7202}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00a9 2026 The Federalist, A wholly independent division of FDRLST Media.\", \"from\": 7205, \"to\": 7274, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"\\u00a9\", \"from\": 7205, \"to\": 7206}, {\"ngram\": \"The Federalist\", \"from\": 7212, \"to\": 7226}, {\"ngram\": \"A wholly independent division\", \"from\": 7228, \"to\": 7257}, {\"ngram\": \"FDRLST Media\", \"from\": 7261, \"to\": 7273}]}, {\"sentence\": \"All rights reserved.\", \"from\": 7275, \"to\": 7295, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"